    "abstract": "Markdown Markup based on <a target=_blank href=https://github.com/showdownjs/showdown rel=noopener> Showdown </a> and <a target=_blank href='https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown' rel='noopener'>Markdown Syntax</a>",
    "description": "Markdown is something like the opposite of markup (HTML, XML, SGML, ...) and can simplify text editing. This Markdown <em>ccm</em> component delivers HTML Tags to write markup directly into your HTML file. It is based on <a target=_blank href=https://github.com/showdownjs/showdown rel=noopener> Showdown </a>. For the syntax of Markdown see <a target=_blank href=http://demo.showdownjs.com/ rel=noopener> demo.showdownjs.com </a> and <a target=_blank href='https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Markdown' rel='noopener'>Wikipedia on Markdown</a>. An editor is provided as well, see the showdown <em>ccm</em> component.<br><h1>Example:</h1><pre style=\"background-color:#ffffff;color:#000000;font-family:'Menlo';font-size:10.5pt;\"><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">script </span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">src=</span><span style=\"color:#008000;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">\"ccm.markdown.js\"</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">script</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span><br><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">ccm-markdown</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span><br># Hello Markdown<br>The text is here.<br><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">ccm-markdown</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">ccm-markdown </span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">markdown=</span><span style=\"color:#008000;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">\"# Hello Markdown\"</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span><br><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">ccm-markdown</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span><br><br><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">ccm-markdown </span><span style=\"color:#0000ff;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">markdown=</span><span style=\"color:#008000;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">\"# Hello Markdown 1\"</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span><br># Hello Markdown 2 is not show because of attribute<br><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&lt;/</span><span style=\"color:#000080;background-color:#efefef;font-weight:bold;\">ccm-markdown</span><span style=\"background-color:#efefef;\">&gt;</span></pre>",
